OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with rain. This soon
OL,6,Fturns to patchy drizzle as bright
OL,7,Fspells develop during the morning.
OL,8,FBright or sunny spells develop as the
OL,9,Fdrizzle clears to the occasional
OL,10,Fshower from the late morning.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FBright spells and the odd
OL,13,Fshower die during the evening. Cloud
OL,14,Fwill spread east from the late evening
OL,15,Fwith drizzle following into the west
OL,16,Fafter midnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
