OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FDry and bright in the
OL,6,Fnortheast at first. Cloud and rain,
OL,7,Fsome heavy, soon spread northeast
OL,8,Fbefore clearing in the southwest later
OL,9,Fin the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FOutbreaks
OL,12,Fof locally heavy rain spread northeast
OL,13,FFriday. This clears to patchy and
OL,14,Fshowery rain Saturday. The rain clears
OL,15,Fovernight to leave Sunday dry with
OL,16,Fsunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
